 "html": "<h2><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-5690 size-full\" src=\"/media/uploads/2019/09/Maklik-met-Marinda-Kaasskons.png\" alt width=\"640\" height=\"640\" srcset=\"/media/uploads/2019/09/Maklik-met-Marinda-Kaasskons.png 640w, /media/uploads/2019/09/Maklik-met-Marinda-Kaasskons-300x300.png 300w, /media/uploads/2019/09/Maklik-met-Marinda-Kaasskons-100x100.png 100w, /media/uploads/2019/09/Maklik-met-Marinda-Kaasskons-600x600.png 600w, /media/uploads/2019/09/Maklik-met-Marinda-Kaasskons-150x150.png 150w, /media/uploads/2019/09/Maklik-met-Marinda-Kaasskons-530x530.png 530w, /media/uploads/2019/09/Maklik-met-Marinda-Kaasskons-500x500.png 500w, /media/uploads/2019/09/Maklik-met-Marinda-Kaasskons-380x380.png 380w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px\"></h2>\n<h2><strong>Bestanddele:</strong></h2>\n<ul>\n<li>500 ml bruismeel</li>\n<li>500 ml gerasperde kaas</li>\n<li>500 ml melk</li>\n<li>5 ml sout</li>\n<li>10 ml Rooipeper of soveel jy kan vat</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>Metode:</h2>\n<p>Meng alles saam</p>\n<p>Skep in kolwyntjiepannetjie en strooi kaas oor</p>\n<p>Bak vir 20 min by 180 grade</p>\n<p>Vinnig en lekker.</p>\n<hr>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>",
